1
00:00:00,310 --> 00:00:01,310
(All people, incidents,
and backgrounds...)

2
00:00:01,310 --> 00:00:02,370
(in this drama are fictitious
and unrelated to reality.)

3
00:00:02,370 --> 00:00:03,380
(Also, children were filmed
under production guidelines.)

4
00:00:10,680 --> 00:00:11,680
Min Jun.

5
00:00:16,190 --> 00:00:17,190
What's wrong?

6
00:00:17,620 --> 00:00:19,520
Is it your headache again?
Is it bad?

7
00:00:25,660 --> 00:00:26,660
Baek Jin Ju.

8
00:00:28,700 --> 00:00:30,770
- What?
- Who's Baek Jin Ju?

9
00:00:31,170 --> 00:00:35,010
I want to know why I used
to refer to Chloe as Baek Jin Ju.

10
00:00:36,140 --> 00:00:37,280
What memory is this?

11
00:00:45,350 --> 00:00:48,150
Goodness, looks like this is going
to be a whirlwind wedding.

12
00:00:50,390 --> 00:00:51,860
We can take our time
with everything else.

13
00:00:52,290 --> 00:00:54,190
I'll get ready
for the ceremony first.

14
00:00:54,390 --> 00:00:56,030
Yes, that's a good idea.

15
00:00:56,660 --> 00:00:58,330
You heard
what Kim Myung Hui said, right?

16
00:00:58,400 --> 00:01:00,930
The joint venture and succession
hinge on this marriage.

17
00:01:00,930 --> 00:01:03,700
It's better to get it done quickly
before Kim Myung Hui interferes.

18
00:01:05,970 --> 00:01:06,970
Are you okay with that?

19
00:01:09,140 --> 00:01:11,580
Why? Is it moving too fast for you?

20
00:01:13,550 --> 00:01:15,580
No, not at all.

21
00:01:16,110 --> 00:01:18,180
I wanted to rush things
from the very beginning.

22
00:01:18,680 --> 00:01:21,250
I want to join the Adele family
as soon as possible.

23
00:01:22,050 --> 00:01:25,220
There's a lot to do
if he's going to take over Adele.

24
00:01:25,420 --> 00:01:27,990
You always know just what to say.

25
00:01:28,930 --> 00:01:31,330
We need to work hard
to make my son chairman.

26
00:01:33,200 --> 00:01:36,940
You know, I like you a lot better
without your memories.

27
00:01:40,170 --> 00:01:41,470
You're really growing on me.

28
00:01:51,720 --> 00:01:55,320
Once we're married
and the development project starts,

29
00:01:56,720 --> 00:01:58,320
I'll become the chairman.

30
00:01:59,220 --> 00:02:01,030
Then I'll expose
my father's crimes...

31
00:02:04,430 --> 00:02:06,100
and immediately hand over
the chairmanship to you.

32
00:02:07,000 --> 00:02:08,000
Right.

33
00:02:08,630 --> 00:02:09,870
This marriage is the first step...

34
00:02:10,540 --> 00:02:14,270
toward gaining the influence
and power I need to become chairman.

35
00:02:18,280 --> 00:02:19,910
(Chairman Park Tae Ho)

36
00:02:21,150 --> 00:02:22,810
It was Baek Jin Ju, not you.

37
00:02:23,210 --> 00:02:26,420
The person I loved, the one
who was by my side, wasn't you.

38
00:02:30,360 --> 00:02:31,360
That's right.

39
00:02:32,190 --> 00:02:33,420
You and Baek Jin Ju.

40
00:02:34,690 --> 00:02:36,060
You were in love.

41
00:02:37,860 --> 00:02:41,400
So you've been lying to me
this whole time?

42
00:02:47,910 --> 00:02:48,910
What about Chloe?

43
00:02:49,210 --> 00:02:51,680
Don't tell me Chloe is Baek Jin Ju.

44
00:02:51,680 --> 00:02:53,550
Baek Jin Ju died.

45
00:02:55,050 --> 00:02:56,110
What?

46
00:02:56,380 --> 00:02:58,020
I didn't lie to you about anything.

47
00:02:58,520 --> 00:03:00,890
We got together
after Baek Jin Ju died.

48
00:03:01,690 --> 00:03:04,120
Chloe is just someone
who looks like her,

49
00:03:04,590 --> 00:03:06,020
and you already
confirmed that yourself.

50
00:03:06,090 --> 00:03:07,790
Then why are you only
telling me this now?

51
00:03:08,730 --> 00:03:11,530
You kept me from knowing
about Baek Jin Ju and Chloe,

52
00:03:11,530 --> 00:03:13,700
and you lied about them.

53
00:03:13,700 --> 00:03:15,200
Because it wasn't important.

54
00:03:16,300 --> 00:03:18,570
Telling someone with amnesia
about a dead person...

55
00:03:19,040 --> 00:03:20,970
wouldn't have changed a thing.

56
00:03:21,640 --> 00:03:24,740
Because the one you love now is me,
not Baek Jin Ju.

57
00:03:27,580 --> 00:03:31,780
I was just trying
to spare you the pain.

58
00:03:32,250 --> 00:03:34,950
I wanted to protect you
while you were confused by amnesia.

59
00:03:38,060 --> 00:03:39,060
Min Jun.

60
00:03:39,790 --> 00:03:41,430
You can't do this to me.

61
00:03:41,960 --> 00:03:44,700
We were so in love
we were planning to get married.

62
00:03:46,330 --> 00:03:48,930
How can you doubt me just because
you remembered someone who's dead?

63
00:03:51,300 --> 00:03:53,200
Please trust me, Min Jun.

64
00:04:00,510 --> 00:04:01,510
I'm sorry.

65
00:04:02,480 --> 00:04:04,220
I think I need some time to think.

66
00:04:07,520 --> 00:04:08,520
Park Min Jun!

67
00:04:16,390 --> 00:04:17,630
Is he starting to remember Jin Ju...

68
00:04:18,400 --> 00:04:20,060
and everything about her?

69
00:04:22,400 --> 00:04:23,400
What do I do?

70
00:04:24,070 --> 00:04:26,240
I can't let him regain his memories.

71
00:04:27,570 --> 00:04:28,970
What am I supposed to do?

72
00:04:38,580 --> 00:04:40,920
What's the truth
and what are the lies?

73
00:04:42,590 --> 00:04:44,090
Baek Jin Ju, Chloe...

74
00:04:44,860 --> 00:04:45,860
What's going on?

75
00:05:00,810 --> 00:05:01,970
Can we help you?

76
00:05:02,710 --> 00:05:03,840
Were we, by any chance...

77
00:05:05,080 --> 00:05:06,080
Sir.

78
00:05:10,050 --> 00:05:11,520
President Kim is looking for you.

79
00:05:12,450 --> 00:05:15,150
- My mother?
- It's probably about our wedding.

80
00:05:17,220 --> 00:05:18,290
This weekend,

81
00:05:19,890 --> 00:05:20,930
Chloe and I...

82
00:05:23,260 --> 00:05:24,260
are getting married.

83
00:05:27,200 --> 00:05:28,200
What?

84
00:05:34,140 --> 00:05:35,410
We should get going.

85
00:05:37,110 --> 00:05:38,880
All the wedding planning...

86
00:05:40,010 --> 00:05:41,010
has us swamped.

87
00:06:00,830 --> 00:06:03,270
So you deliberately
provoked Oh Jung Ran...

88
00:06:03,530 --> 00:06:05,900
to make her rush the wedding?

89
00:06:07,170 --> 00:06:09,170
To get out from under her watch,

90
00:06:09,440 --> 00:06:10,910
the wedding will be
the perfect distraction.

91
00:06:11,240 --> 00:06:14,110
And we have to act fast
before the chairman gets any worse.

92
00:06:15,180 --> 00:06:16,650
We'll have to act fast, too.

93
00:06:16,880 --> 00:06:19,080
First, I need to meet
with Butler Ok.

94
00:06:19,250 --> 00:06:21,090
Yes, I'll contact her.

95
00:06:27,490 --> 00:06:28,930
Min Jun, on that day...

96
00:06:31,060 --> 00:06:32,060
Min Jun.

97
00:06:32,660 --> 00:06:33,970
What's on your mind?

98
00:06:35,570 --> 00:06:36,570
I'm sorry.

99
00:06:37,070 --> 00:06:39,340
The news of the wedding came
as such a surprise.

100
00:06:39,970 --> 00:06:43,310
Does that wedding
bother you that much?

101
00:06:44,640 --> 00:06:47,710
What bothers me isn't the wedding,
but Chloe.

102
00:06:48,510 --> 00:06:50,780
At first, I thought she was
just Hyun Jun's fiancee,

103
00:06:50,850 --> 00:06:54,650
but then I learned she tried
to leak company secrets.

104
00:06:56,320 --> 00:06:59,260
What if Chloe and I had some kind
of special relationship...

105
00:06:59,620 --> 00:07:01,290
before I lost my memory?

106
00:07:01,290 --> 00:07:04,430
Chloe wanted to marry Hyun Jun.

107
00:07:06,600 --> 00:07:10,070
Given that she still feels the same
even after losing her memory,

108
00:07:10,400 --> 00:07:11,900
it means they're destined
to be together.

109
00:07:13,170 --> 00:07:17,280
Even after all that, she still
hasn't mentioned Baek Jin Ju.

110
00:07:18,580 --> 00:07:20,210
Baek Jin Ju and Chloe.

111
00:07:21,050 --> 00:07:24,150
Does my mother not know
about them...

112
00:07:24,350 --> 00:07:28,920
or is she deliberately hiding it,
just like Choi Yu Na?

113
00:08:00,720 --> 00:08:01,920
Dad...

114
00:08:04,060 --> 00:08:05,260
I'm getting married.

115
00:08:08,630 --> 00:08:10,360
You said Adele wasn't
the place for me,

116
00:08:10,800 --> 00:08:13,360
that I didn't belong there.

117
00:08:16,100 --> 00:08:17,940
But I didn't listen to you, Dad.

118
00:08:18,970 --> 00:08:21,670
I know James is concerned,

119
00:08:23,070 --> 00:08:24,480
but I'm still going
to see this through.

120
00:08:29,580 --> 00:08:31,220
How far do I have to go,

121
00:08:31,550 --> 00:08:33,520
how much more do I have to take,

122
00:08:34,820 --> 00:08:38,590
before I can finally put an end
to this agonizing injustice?

123
00:08:44,730 --> 00:08:46,360
Even now...

124
00:08:46,430 --> 00:08:47,830
(Hanbit High School
62nd Graduation Ceremony)

125
00:08:47,900 --> 00:08:50,300
I miss you so much, Dad,

126
00:08:51,270 --> 00:08:52,570
and everything hurts so much.

127
00:08:55,710 --> 00:08:58,680
Will it ever end, Dad?

128
00:09:19,660 --> 00:09:22,500
How long will it take
for the antidote treatment to work?

129
00:09:23,000 --> 00:09:26,200
They said that,
with specialized intensive care,

130
00:09:26,200 --> 00:09:30,040
regaining consciousness
would take only 3 to 4 hours.

131
00:09:30,640 --> 00:09:31,980
Three to four hours?

132
00:09:32,040 --> 00:09:34,910
Even if Oh Jung Ran
attends the wedding,

133
00:09:35,480 --> 00:09:37,550
she'll leave
her security team behind.

134
00:09:38,080 --> 00:09:40,520
So, to get Chairman Park out
of the house,

135
00:09:40,590 --> 00:09:44,190
you'll need plenty of people
on your side as well.

136
00:09:49,390 --> 00:09:51,230
I've brought Butler Ok.

137
00:09:55,830 --> 00:09:56,930
Please, come in.

138
00:09:59,340 --> 00:10:01,470
She's our former housekeeper.

139
00:10:01,470 --> 00:10:02,810
Is she also...

140
00:10:03,540 --> 00:10:06,810
going to help you
get Chairman Park out?

141
00:10:06,940 --> 00:10:09,480
She'll be helping us with something
even more important.

142
00:10:23,830 --> 00:10:24,830
I...

143
00:10:26,100 --> 00:10:27,300
remembered something.

144
00:10:28,170 --> 00:10:31,140
Something neither our mother
nor Choi Yu Na told me about.

145
00:10:31,570 --> 00:10:33,540
So now I know for sure.

146
00:10:34,040 --> 00:10:38,180
You were the only one
who ever told me the truth.

147
00:10:39,310 --> 00:10:42,810
- The truth?
- You warned me about Yu Na.

148
00:10:42,950 --> 00:10:45,880
That's why I came to you
for answers...

149
00:10:46,620 --> 00:10:49,620
about Baek Jin Ju and Chloe.

150
00:10:53,290 --> 00:10:55,090
From the look on your face,

151
00:10:55,530 --> 00:10:57,630
you know about Baek Jin Ju too.

152
00:10:59,060 --> 00:11:01,500
- Baek Jin Ju is...
- Is Chloe actually Baek Jin Ju?

153
00:11:04,600 --> 00:11:06,400
What is it you remember, exactly?

154
00:11:06,870 --> 00:11:09,370
Don't change the subject.
Just give me a straight answer.

155
00:11:09,470 --> 00:11:11,040
It's not a hard question.

156
00:11:11,940 --> 00:11:13,310
Is Chloe...

157
00:11:14,150 --> 00:11:15,250
Baek Jin Ju?

158
00:11:19,050 --> 00:11:20,120
No.

159
00:11:27,220 --> 00:11:28,960
You have that same look
on your face.

160
00:11:30,330 --> 00:11:32,160
It's the one Choi Yu Na had.

161
00:11:38,670 --> 00:11:39,870
The wedding is soon.

162
00:11:40,370 --> 00:11:41,740
There's no turning back now.

163
00:11:42,870 --> 00:11:45,780
Baek Jin Ju chose me, not you.

164
00:11:46,210 --> 00:11:48,080
So whatever Baek Jin Ju wants,

165
00:11:51,220 --> 00:11:52,580
I'll see it through with her.

166
00:12:04,130 --> 00:12:05,130
Yu Na.

167
00:12:06,860 --> 00:12:10,500
The cleaners delivered
these clothes for you.

168
00:12:11,000 --> 00:12:14,210
These are the types of clothes
Jin Ju liked.

169
00:12:14,270 --> 00:12:17,680
When are you going
to stop imitating her?

170
00:12:17,680 --> 00:12:19,110
Gosh, this is heavy.

171
00:12:19,680 --> 00:12:20,680
Goodness.

172
00:12:21,180 --> 00:12:22,480
- What the...
- Hey!

173
00:12:22,680 --> 00:12:26,050
Are you kidding me?
What was that just now?

174
00:12:27,590 --> 00:12:28,850
Park Min Jun.

175
00:12:29,690 --> 00:12:31,620
He remembered Baek Jin Ju.

176
00:12:32,290 --> 00:12:33,520
- What?
- What?

177
00:12:33,590 --> 00:12:36,430
It's all because you and Dad
brought her up.

178
00:12:36,760 --> 00:12:39,760
Dressing like Jin Ju is useless now.

179
00:12:40,700 --> 00:12:43,970
From now on, he can't be reminded
of her in any way.

180
00:12:44,030 --> 00:12:46,040
So what now?

181
00:12:46,140 --> 00:12:50,610
Goodness me.
You haven't completely won him over,

182
00:12:50,710 --> 00:12:53,010
so what if
all his memories come back?

183
00:12:53,340 --> 00:12:56,910
If I'd known this would happen,
I'd have told you to have his baby.

184
00:12:58,480 --> 00:13:00,350
You're both useless,

185
00:13:00,820 --> 00:13:04,020
- so get out. Out!
- My goodness. Honestly.

186
00:13:04,220 --> 00:13:06,420
- Fine, we're going.
- Goodness.

187
00:13:06,790 --> 00:13:07,790
Good grief.

188
00:13:15,400 --> 00:13:16,600
I was so close.

189
00:13:17,940 --> 00:13:20,170
I had almost won his heart.

190
00:13:22,310 --> 00:13:24,510
And once again,
Baek Jin Ju got in the way.

191
00:13:26,840 --> 00:13:29,480
Baek Jin Ju!

192
00:13:31,180 --> 00:13:32,180
Just you wait.

193
00:13:33,250 --> 00:13:34,850
I'm not going to let him
slip away like this.

194
00:13:36,020 --> 00:13:39,060
Somehow, I'll stop his memories
from coming back,

195
00:13:40,720 --> 00:13:42,090
and I'll protect what's mine.

196
00:13:48,200 --> 00:13:50,030
(Adele)

197
00:13:50,370 --> 00:13:52,670
Let's go away together
for the weekend.

198
00:13:53,870 --> 00:13:56,140
I've already booked the hotel
and everything.

199
00:13:57,310 --> 00:13:59,610
Wouldn't it be nice
to get away from all this...

200
00:13:59,610 --> 00:14:01,180
and forget
your uncomfortable feelings?

201
00:14:01,750 --> 00:14:02,750
No.

202
00:14:04,780 --> 00:14:06,350
You should probably go alone.

203
00:14:08,690 --> 00:14:10,790
Are you still upset about yesterday?

204
00:14:11,590 --> 00:14:13,990
Hyun Jun and Chloe are
getting married this weekend.

205
00:14:14,090 --> 00:14:16,530
What? They're getting married?

206
00:14:16,590 --> 00:14:18,100
So suddenly?

207
00:14:27,400 --> 00:14:29,540
Hey, Park Min Jun.

208
00:14:37,310 --> 00:14:38,380
Are you perhaps Baek...

209
00:14:41,620 --> 00:14:44,760
Chloe, am I not part
of any of your memories?

210
00:14:46,890 --> 00:14:50,760
Because I feel like
you're somewhere in mine.

211
00:14:50,890 --> 00:14:55,100
Whenever I see you, I get confused
and I can't get you out of my head.

212
00:14:55,600 --> 00:14:56,730
What about you?

213
00:14:57,330 --> 00:15:00,240
Has anything come back to you
since the accident?

214
00:15:01,370 --> 00:15:02,870
Don't you remember me...

215
00:15:04,810 --> 00:15:06,280
or have any feelings for me?

216
00:15:09,080 --> 00:15:10,080
No.

217
00:15:11,080 --> 00:15:14,180
I have no memories of you
and no feelings for you.

218
00:15:16,150 --> 00:15:18,960
When it comes to you, I feel...

219
00:15:21,390 --> 00:15:22,390
nothing.

220
00:16:16,010 --> 00:16:17,780
This is your last chance.

221
00:16:20,120 --> 00:16:21,120
What?

222
00:16:21,720 --> 00:16:22,820
Tomorrow,

223
00:16:23,890 --> 00:16:25,690
once the ceremony begins,

224
00:16:25,920 --> 00:16:29,060
I'm going all in,
and there's no stopping me.

225
00:16:30,690 --> 00:16:32,160
If you want to call this off,

226
00:16:35,070 --> 00:16:36,370
tell me now.

227
00:16:40,570 --> 00:16:41,570
No.

228
00:16:43,570 --> 00:16:45,240
I'm not calling it off.

229
00:16:46,710 --> 00:16:47,810
In that case,

230
00:16:48,750 --> 00:16:50,680
I guess I don't have
to back out either.

231
00:17:03,390 --> 00:17:05,500
Since this is a marriage
for revenge,

232
00:17:05,900 --> 00:17:08,270
I wasn't sure if I should propose,

233
00:17:10,730 --> 00:17:12,400
so I gave it a lot of thought.

234
00:17:15,570 --> 00:17:16,740
But still,

235
00:17:18,910 --> 00:17:21,310
even if this whole marriage
is a sham,

236
00:17:22,880 --> 00:17:24,720
my feelings for you are real.

237
00:17:37,590 --> 00:17:41,300
I wanted to make
a proper confession...

238
00:17:43,930 --> 00:17:45,440
of my love for you.

239
00:17:51,180 --> 00:17:52,180
I love you.

240
00:17:54,610 --> 00:17:55,710
Baek Jin Ju.

241
00:18:19,740 --> 00:18:21,340
I know that you mean it.

242
00:18:23,610 --> 00:18:25,180
I really do.

243
00:18:27,540 --> 00:18:29,350
And for that, I'm grateful.

244
00:18:31,680 --> 00:18:32,680
And I'm sorry.

245
00:18:35,420 --> 00:18:38,420
But for a marriage like ours,

246
00:18:38,920 --> 00:18:41,230
a proposal like this
isn't appropriate.

247
00:18:52,140 --> 00:18:53,540
I...

248
00:18:54,770 --> 00:18:56,870
I got carried away again.

249
00:18:59,780 --> 00:19:01,310
I just...

250
00:19:03,610 --> 00:19:04,780
wanted to do...

251
00:19:06,620 --> 00:19:08,650
something nice for you.

252
00:19:13,090 --> 00:19:14,090
Then...

253
00:19:15,690 --> 00:19:17,160
how about doing
something else for me?

254
00:19:19,830 --> 00:19:20,830
Something else?

255
00:19:22,170 --> 00:19:24,170
I want to see Chairman Park.

256
00:19:28,710 --> 00:19:29,710
Right.

257
00:19:31,840 --> 00:19:33,110
For a marriage like ours,

258
00:19:34,210 --> 00:19:35,580
that request is more fitting.

259
00:19:45,260 --> 00:19:47,690
Technically,
visitors aren't allowed,

260
00:19:48,190 --> 00:19:51,260
but I'll make an exception
for you two.

261
00:19:52,200 --> 00:19:53,960
You wanted to see your father...

262
00:19:54,500 --> 00:19:58,370
before you get married, right?

263
00:19:59,500 --> 00:20:01,410
I guess so.

264
00:20:04,510 --> 00:20:07,140
Your son is getting married.

265
00:20:08,680 --> 00:20:10,510
You're lucky to have him visit you.

266
00:20:14,480 --> 00:20:16,990
I need to have a word with you,
Mr. Song.

267
00:20:17,920 --> 00:20:19,420
What, me?

268
00:20:20,860 --> 00:20:22,430
Just you and me?

269
00:20:25,900 --> 00:20:27,970
- Let's go.
- Okay, sure.

270
00:20:38,940 --> 00:20:40,940
Just because
you're incapacitated like this,

271
00:20:42,110 --> 00:20:46,480
and just because karma has punished you
for your evil deeds,

272
00:20:48,150 --> 00:20:49,690
do you think this is over?

273
00:20:51,420 --> 00:20:52,660
No.

274
00:20:53,420 --> 00:20:55,060
You still...

275
00:20:55,690 --> 00:20:57,730
haven't lost a single thing.

276
00:20:58,400 --> 00:20:59,760
You're still alive,

277
00:20:59,760 --> 00:21:01,930
and Adele, which you cherish
as much as your own life,

278
00:21:02,000 --> 00:21:03,500
is still completely yours.

279
00:21:05,900 --> 00:21:07,740
It remains untouched,
just as the injustice...

280
00:21:09,570 --> 00:21:11,110
done to my father
remains unresolved.

281
00:21:14,710 --> 00:21:17,950
Tomorrow, I'll become
your daughter-in-law,

282
00:21:18,380 --> 00:21:20,350
and a member of the Adele family.

283
00:21:21,620 --> 00:21:25,920
I'll watch you fade away
as I take Adele from you.

284
00:21:26,190 --> 00:21:28,260
I'll uncover the truth
of what happened seven years ago,

285
00:21:29,190 --> 00:21:31,500
so you will die branded
as a murderer.

286
00:21:35,030 --> 00:21:38,700
So don't you dare die before then.

287
00:21:38,970 --> 00:21:41,240
Watch everything unravel,
Chairman Park.

288
00:21:45,510 --> 00:21:46,580
I mean,

289
00:21:47,380 --> 00:21:48,610
Father.

290
00:22:01,430 --> 00:22:03,430
- Congratulations.
- Thank you very much.

291
00:22:04,900 --> 00:22:06,860
I'm so glad you could make it.

292
00:22:08,030 --> 00:22:10,330
Because the chairman is recovering
from a health issue,

293
00:22:10,330 --> 00:22:12,670
we decided to go ahead with...

294
00:22:12,740 --> 00:22:15,070
- our son's wedding immediately.
- How thoughtful of you.

295
00:22:15,140 --> 00:22:16,640
- Thank you.
- Congratulations.

296
00:22:16,710 --> 00:22:18,280
- Thank you.
- Please, head on in.

297
00:22:19,080 --> 00:22:20,310
Goodness. Congratulations.

298
00:22:22,510 --> 00:22:24,150
- Hurry inside already.
- Right.

299
00:22:41,830 --> 00:22:44,630
He didn't even congratulate you,
so why bother with that jerk?

300
00:22:45,570 --> 00:22:47,440
Today isn't just any wedding.

301
00:22:47,740 --> 00:22:50,340
This is your chance to make a name
for yourself as Adele's successor.

302
00:22:51,140 --> 00:22:54,580
Forget about Park Min Jun
and stay right by my side.

303
00:22:58,120 --> 00:23:00,250
Welcome!

304
00:23:22,840 --> 00:23:23,970
My gosh.

305
00:23:24,980 --> 00:23:26,480
Just look at you.

306
00:23:27,840 --> 00:23:29,650
You are so, so beautiful.

307
00:23:30,610 --> 00:23:33,620
Then don't cry. Smile for me.

308
00:23:34,280 --> 00:23:35,590
Of course.

309
00:23:36,550 --> 00:23:37,650
I should be smiling.

310
00:23:40,760 --> 00:23:41,760
Oh, my.

311
00:23:49,100 --> 00:23:50,100
Goodness.

312
00:23:53,470 --> 00:23:54,470
Oh, dear.

313
00:24:31,810 --> 00:24:34,950
Do you have any more questions?

314
00:24:34,950 --> 00:24:36,680
How were you so certain?

315
00:24:37,250 --> 00:24:39,950
You lost your memory,
just like I did.

316
00:24:39,980 --> 00:24:44,620
You must have been confused about
what was true and what wasn't.

317
00:24:45,760 --> 00:24:49,130
So how could you decide
to go through with this marriage?

318
00:24:50,960 --> 00:24:52,430
Because I made a choice.

319
00:24:53,930 --> 00:24:58,170
It's a decision I made
before I lost my memory.

320
00:24:58,770 --> 00:25:00,170
I'm choosing to trust my past self.

321
00:25:00,240 --> 00:25:04,340
You saw what Hyun Jun's mother did.
Doesn't that matter to you?

322
00:25:04,440 --> 00:25:05,880
It doesn't.

323
00:25:08,510 --> 00:25:12,380
I guess it's because
I'm just like her.

324
00:25:13,180 --> 00:25:15,290
Because in order to get what I want,

325
00:25:15,950 --> 00:25:18,620
I believe the ends...

326
00:25:20,360 --> 00:25:21,690
justify the means.

327
00:25:25,830 --> 00:25:30,030
So were my feelings for you
all in my head?

328
00:25:30,870 --> 00:25:33,170
Is Baek Jin Ju really dead,

329
00:25:33,570 --> 00:25:37,010
and you're just a look-alike?

330
00:25:39,480 --> 00:25:43,950
Right. Maybe that's who you are.

331
00:25:46,420 --> 00:25:47,420
Then...

332
00:25:52,920 --> 00:25:55,660
Yes. That's exactly who I am.

333
00:25:56,360 --> 00:26:00,330
Someone who'll do anything
to achieve her goals.

334
00:26:01,630 --> 00:26:04,030
That must be why
I'm leaving you behind...

335
00:26:04,600 --> 00:26:06,640
and choosing this marriage.

336
00:26:09,210 --> 00:26:10,710
You made it.

337
00:26:18,850 --> 00:26:21,250
- Hello.
- Hello.

338
00:26:21,380 --> 00:26:22,420
You're here, ma'am.

339
00:26:31,730 --> 00:26:33,260
Did you greet the groom?

340
00:26:33,530 --> 00:26:35,400
I made a quick appearance.

341
00:26:35,430 --> 00:26:37,030
I'm going to head over
to Father now.

342
00:26:38,030 --> 00:26:39,840
Is Chloe still on your mind?

343
00:26:40,800 --> 00:26:42,740
You should head inside.
I'll be in touch.

344
00:26:43,970 --> 00:26:45,780
Okay, be careful.

345
00:26:46,180 --> 00:26:47,180
I will.

346
00:26:55,990 --> 00:26:57,150
I can't go that far.

347
00:27:02,860 --> 00:27:04,860
In any case,
you're part of this family too,

348
00:27:05,200 --> 00:27:06,700
so stay put until it's over.

349
00:27:10,930 --> 00:27:12,040
Part of this family?

350
00:27:12,670 --> 00:27:14,370
Are you finally acknowledging me?

351
00:27:15,570 --> 00:27:19,310
Why? Are you afraid
I'll pull something behind your back?

352
00:27:20,080 --> 00:27:23,650
Is that why you put me
where you could always see me?

353
00:27:25,450 --> 00:27:26,450
Fine.

354
00:27:27,250 --> 00:27:29,490
I won't let you ruin my mood
on a day like this.

355
00:27:31,020 --> 00:27:34,360
You think I'm going to take the bait
on a happy day like this?

356
00:27:35,490 --> 00:27:37,860
Just tell your son to hurry up
and take his seat.

357
00:27:48,940 --> 00:27:50,710
The wedding
of your one and only son.

358
00:27:51,170 --> 00:27:53,510
Yes, on this wonderful day,

359
00:27:54,210 --> 00:27:55,550
on this very happy day,

360
00:27:56,480 --> 00:27:59,650
your life as you know it
is about to end.

361
00:28:12,430 --> 00:28:13,660
My dear Hyun Jun.

362
00:28:14,800 --> 00:28:17,230
He must look incredible
in his tuxedo.

363
00:28:18,770 --> 00:28:21,400
It's a once-in-a-lifetime moment,

364
00:28:23,340 --> 00:28:24,470
and I can't be there to see it.

365
00:28:26,880 --> 00:28:27,880
But still,

366
00:28:28,310 --> 00:28:30,850
he's getting to marry
the person he loves,

367
00:28:31,610 --> 00:28:32,620
so that's a relief.

368
00:28:38,590 --> 00:28:40,090
Mrs. Ok.

369
00:28:41,120 --> 00:28:43,230
Why are you back here again?

370
00:28:43,230 --> 00:28:45,300
It's a good thing
Jung Ran isn't here.

371
00:28:45,360 --> 00:28:47,730
If she were,
you'd be in serious trouble.

372
00:28:48,060 --> 00:28:49,770
I left in such a hurry
the other day...

373
00:28:50,100 --> 00:28:51,800
that I forgot a few things.

374
00:28:54,840 --> 00:28:58,040
It seems you've added more staff
because of the chairman.

375
00:28:58,440 --> 00:29:00,680
Right. Well, I guess so.

376
00:29:01,740 --> 00:29:03,450
You should get your things and go.

377
00:29:03,450 --> 00:29:08,820
Hold on. You and the guards
look exhausted.

378
00:29:09,190 --> 00:29:12,160
Since I'm here,
let me get everyone a cold drink.

379
00:29:12,290 --> 00:29:15,430
What?
No, that's really not necessary.

380
00:29:15,430 --> 00:29:18,060
Come on.
You're at least able to sit down,

381
00:29:18,060 --> 00:29:20,360
but those two have been standing
the whole time.

382
00:29:20,500 --> 00:29:23,400
Have a drink
and take a ten-minute break.

383
00:29:23,400 --> 00:29:24,400
But...

384
00:29:25,540 --> 00:29:26,770
We're fine, ma'am.

385
00:29:26,870 --> 00:29:28,370
Yes, it's against the rules.

386
00:29:28,370 --> 00:29:33,380
The mother in me feels for you,
so I insist.

387
00:29:33,610 --> 00:29:36,080
I'll be right back with some drinks.

388
00:29:36,410 --> 00:29:37,510
But...

389
00:29:38,280 --> 00:29:40,250
For crying out loud.

390
00:30:17,150 --> 00:30:19,620
Mrs. Ok,
you pulled it off perfectly.

391
00:30:19,720 --> 00:30:22,390
Fortunately,
they weren't too suspicious of me.

392
00:30:22,730 --> 00:30:25,630
Thanks to the sleeping pills,
they're dead to the world.

393
00:30:25,760 --> 00:30:28,830
You did a great job.
We'll take it from here.

394
00:30:29,530 --> 00:30:33,700
Things could get dangerous,
so you should leave now.

395
00:30:34,040 --> 00:30:36,940
Okay, I will. Please be careful.

396
00:30:40,780 --> 00:30:42,850
All right, let's get started.

397
00:30:42,850 --> 00:30:44,750
Okay, we'll handle things over here.

398
00:30:45,080 --> 00:30:46,080
Right.

399
00:30:46,980 --> 00:30:49,020
We're counting on you.
Shall we, Doctor?

400
00:30:49,020 --> 00:30:50,050
Sure.

401
00:30:58,600 --> 00:31:02,330
Doctor,
even if the unexpected happens,

402
00:31:03,200 --> 00:31:04,430
you must continue the treatment.

403
00:31:04,730 --> 00:31:05,970
Yes, I understand.

404
00:31:13,440 --> 00:31:14,440
Remove them.

405
00:31:20,050 --> 00:31:21,680
All that's left is
to remove Mr. Song, right?

406
00:31:22,020 --> 00:31:26,190
Yes, as Ms. Kim instructed,
we've removed Oh Jung Ran's people.

407
00:31:39,970 --> 00:31:41,540
Instead of moving Chairman Park,

408
00:31:41,970 --> 00:31:45,280
do you have something else planned?

409
00:31:45,940 --> 00:31:48,750
If it will take 3 to 4 hours
for him to regain consciousness,

410
00:31:49,010 --> 00:31:52,450
it'll be better to secure him
than to move him.

411
00:31:53,120 --> 00:31:54,820
While Oh Jung Ran is out
of the house,

412
00:31:55,690 --> 00:31:57,120
we're going to take control of it.

413
00:32:10,870 --> 00:32:12,970
This way. What?

414
00:32:16,540 --> 00:32:18,010
What do you think you're doing?

415
00:32:26,380 --> 00:32:29,090
We're taking over security
from now on.

416
00:32:29,920 --> 00:32:31,520
- As for you, Manager Kang...
- Hey!

417
00:32:33,620 --> 00:32:34,620
Sir!

418
00:32:35,560 --> 00:32:37,160
- Sir!
- Sir!

419
00:32:39,060 --> 00:32:40,060
Sir!

420
00:32:52,340 --> 00:32:53,340
Jin Ju.

421
00:32:54,280 --> 00:32:55,310
Jin Ju.

422
00:32:56,480 --> 00:32:57,480
Jin Ju...

423
00:32:59,920 --> 00:33:01,050
Baek Jin Ju.

424
00:33:03,820 --> 00:33:05,120
Here comes the bride.

425
00:33:21,470 --> 00:33:22,510
Stop!

426
00:33:57,270 --> 00:33:59,280
(Subtitles are provided by KOCOWA.)
